# Breathe ESG Ingestion & Audit Prototype

A comprehensive full-stack prototype built to ingest, normalize, and audit multi-tenant greenhouse gas (GHG) footprint tracking data across fragmented real-world enterprise sources.

## 🚀 Deployed Environments
- **Live Frontend Application UI:** `https://breathe-frontend.onrender.com` *(Replace with your actual Render Frontend Static Site Link)*
- **Live Production API Gateway Server:** `https://breathe-esg-ty4m.onrender.com`

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack & Architecture
- **Backend:** Django 5.x, Django REST Framework (DRF)
- **Frontend:** React (Vite), Axios, Tailwind CSS / Modern CSS Variables
- **Data Ingestion Engine:** Pandas & NumPy for real-world anomaly detection and field alignment overrides.

